                     <interp inst="t18180909-132-off723" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180909-132-cd724" type="crimeDate">24th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-132-off723 t18180909-132-cd724"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-132-off725 t18180909-132-cd724"></join>, in a ship called the Isabella, in the port of London (the same being a port of entry and discharge), 350 yards of printed cotton, value 25l.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
