               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180909-132-person1085">
                  CHARLES 
                  PERROTT
               <interp inst="t18180909-132-person1085" type="surname" value="PERROTT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-132-person1085" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-132-person1085" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Milner, a packer. On the 9th of July I packed printed cottons in a trunk, which were shipped on board the Isabella, in the <placeName id="t18180909-132-crimeloc726">London Docks</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180909-132-crimeloc726" type="placeName" value="London Docks"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180909-132-crimeloc726" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
